quoteText: If you do not receive timely acknowledgment of your complaint from us, or if we have not addressed your complaint to your satisfaction, please contact or visit https://www.privacytrust.com/drs/stackexchange OR PrivacyTrust, Communications House, 26 York Street, London, W1U 6PZ, for more information or to file a complaint.
title: The service provides a complaint mechanism for the handling of personal data
